<L>__{interior helen s sitting room day}
<A>__{mrs. stephens is doing her knitting. the inevitable glass stands on the table beside her. helen is seated opposite, reading from a newspaper.}
<C>__{helen}
<D>__{she was appearing in arthur baden's new film the walls are closing in, starring diane ashley.}
<A>__{close shot of mrs. stephens listening intently.}
<C>__{helen}
